and here's the guy who did it. He got 14 years and he's out in
eight. There ain't no justice.'' _ District Attorney Donald Stahl
of Stanislaus County, Calif., who prosecuted rapist-mutilator Larry
Singleton, freed today after serving eight years of his 14-year
prison sentence.
