of a crime or whether it was buried legally,'' Reus said. ``We
brought in a bulldozer to do some digging of our own but found
nothing.''
   He said seven people already had laimed ownership of the
treasure.
   According to Dutch law, authorities have 30 years to find the
legal owners. If none is found, the gold and jewels will become the
property of the finders.
